stories.title: Cairns sensational as Black Caps power to thrilling victory
stories.summary: A brilliant unbeaten century from Chris Cairns has guided New Zealand to a four wicket victory over South Africa in the countries' VB Series match here at the 'Gabba ground in Brisbane tonight

stories.title: Bond triggers South African batting collapse at Gabba
